Whole months have passed since I
quit the merc life to be a cook...but
finally the head cook approves of me!

rows.label: tlk43300046_06_msg0002
rows.name: I'm now permitted to make a real dish.

rows.label: tlk43300046_06_msg0003
rows.name:
Namely, I'm in charge of
the Roast Meat Tagliata!

rows.label: tlk43300046_06_msg0004
rows.name: Now if I only knew how to make that...
